HEADWORD: Sparkish
<hw>Spark"ish</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Like a spark; airy;
gay.</def> <rj><au>W. Walsh.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Showy; well-dressed; fine.</def>
